ake some Big Tech stocks look like bargains at current prices.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m more excited now than I h=
ave been for a very long time,=E2=80=9D he said in an interview. =E2=80=9CS=
o many industries can benefit, while the arms dealers for AI should benefit=
 even more.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yeah I mean the possibilities are (1) AI takes=
 over the world imminently, which is good for S&amp;P 500 investors=C2=A0<e=
m>qua=C2=A0</em>S&amp;P 500 investors, or (2) it doesn=E2=80=99t, which is =
probably good for most S&amp;P 500 investors <em>qua</em> professional know=
ledge workers whose jobs could get squeezed by AI. Owning Nvidia stock is a=
 decent hedge to getting replaced by an Nvidia-powered=C2=A0robot!</p>
